---Nov 6, 2022 start FE!---

FRONTEND:

react - TS  - RTK - tailwind - rtk query?

1. create-react-app . --template typescript in client folder

2. install tailwind
=> npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer

3. initialize tailwind.config
=> npx tailwindcss init -p


4. configure tailwind.config.js
- in content =>

 content: ["./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}"],
 
5. Add the Tailwind directives to your CSS
- in index.css

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;


6. install rtk
=> npm i @reduxjs/toolkit react-redux

7. install react router and axios and react-toastify
=> npm i react-router-dom axios react-toastify
